#: ../../mainclass.rst:2
msgid "CameraFollowCursorCV"
msgstr "CameraFollowCursorCV"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:1 of
msgid ""
"CameraFollowCursorCV is a class designed to create animated videos that "
"simulate the process of typing code. It animates code line by line and "
"character by character while smoothly moving the camera to follow the "
"cursor, creating a professional-looking coding demonstration."
msgstr ""
"CameraFollowCursorCV 是一个用于创建模拟打字过程的动画视频的类。"
"它逐行逐字符地动画化代码，同时平滑移动镜头跟随光标，"
"打造出专业的代码演示效果。"

#: ../../mainclass.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:4 of
msgid ""
"The code to be animated. **When using a string**, provide a tuple with "
"the first element as ``'string'`` and the second element as the code "
"string. **When using a file**, provide a tuple with the first element as "
"``'file'`` and the second element as the file path."
msgstr ""
"要动画化的代码。**使用字符串时**，提供一个元组，第一个元素为 ``'string'``，"
"第二个元素为代码字符串。**使用文件时**，提供一个元组，第一个元素为 ``'file'``，"
"第二个元素为文件路径。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:6 of
msgid "The programming language of the code."
msgstr "代码的编程语言。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:8 of
msgid "The style for syntax highlighting. Defaults to ``\"material\"``."
msgstr "语法高亮的样式。默认为 ``\"material\"``。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:10 of
msgid "The line spacing for the code. Defaults to :data:`~.DEFAULT_LINE_SPACING`."
msgstr "代码的行间距。默认为 :data:`~.DEFAULT_LINE_SPACING`。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:12 of
msgid ""
"The range of typing intervals between characters. Defaults to "
"(:data:`~.DEFAULT_TYPE_INTERVAL`, :data:`~.DEFAULT_TYPE_INTERVAL`)."
msgstr ""
"字符之间的打字间隔范围。"
"默认为 (:data:`~.DEFAULT_TYPE_INTERVAL`, :data:`~.DEFAULT_TYPE_INTERVAL`)。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:14 of
msgid "The scale factor for the camera. Defaults to 0.5."
msgstr "相机的缩放因子。默认为 0.5。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:16 of
msgid ""
"The name of the output video file. Defaults to "
"``\"CameraFollowCursorCV\"``."
msgstr "输出视频文件的名称。默认为 ``\"CameraFollowCursorCV\"``。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:18 of
msgid "The renderer to use for video rendering. Defaults to ``'cairo'``."
msgstr "用于视频渲染的渲染器。默认为 ``'cairo'``。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV._create_scene:1 of
msgid "Create manim scene to animate code rendering."
msgstr "创建 manim 场景以动画化代码渲染。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.render:1 of
msgid "Render the scene, optionally with console output."
msgstr "渲染场景，可选择是否输出到控制台。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.render:3 of
msgid ""
"Whether to print console output during rendering. Defaults to "
":data:`~.DEFAULT_OUTPUT_VALUE`."
msgstr "渲染期间是否打印控制台输出。默认为 :data:`~.DEFAULT_OUTPUT_VALUE`。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.__getattribute__:1 of
msgid "Return getattr(self, name)."
msgstr "返回 getattr(self, name)。"
